text:

title: Heysel Dress - Navy
text:
Vintage inspired cotton dress from Bellerose with ever so pretty eyelet embroidery. elasticated waist with Peter Pan collar and tear drop neckline. Falls to just below the knee.
Fabric: Shell - 50% Viscose, 50% Rayon Contrast - 100% Viscose. Embroidery tread - 100% Cotton

title: Papyrus Shirt - Metallic Stripe
text:
Cut in a lightweight cotton blend with a multi-coloured metallic stripe, this super cool shirt has a high collar, half button placket and elasticated cuffs. We love the curved hem detail. Tuck into high-waisted denim for a chic day look.
Fabric: 90% Cotton 10% Lurex. Lining 100% Cotton.
Care: Dry clean recommended

title: V-10 Trainer - Extra White
text:
A pair of ecological trainers from Veja made from vegetable-tanned leather with a perforated toe, sitting on top of an Amazonian wild rubber sole with a herringbone tread.
016, Veja introduces the V-10 model to celebrate our 10th anniversary. The V-10 model made out of ecological and sustainable materials stands for 10 ans d’amour. The style comes up a little large.

title: Kimitomo Blouse - Indigo
text:
The Kimitomo blouse a best selling Sessun style crafted here in a super wearable navy. With voluminous short sleeves and chiffon trims this top will work well with denim, shorts or tucked into a skirt. We love the lace inserts on the shoulders and the 3-button detailing.
Fabric: 100% Cotton
Care: 30 delicate wash recommended

This is the first frame ever created for the Pared label. The cat eye with a black handmade acetate frame. Gold deco details at the corners and dark tortoise arms. Solid brown with Cr39 lenses. Gold 'p' temple. German rubber dipped screws. Comes with custom Pared case, lens cloth and warranty card.

title: Greyhound Bag - Black
text:
The Greyhound shoulder bag from Mercules is designed and handmade in a black soft to the touch leather Metal star studs detailing on the front flap, fold over front flap with a magnetic press stud fastening. Adjustable buckle fastened shoulder strap.

title: Nina Shift Dress - Natural
text:
The Nina shift dress is a perfect summer dress, easy and effortless, cut in a soft cotton with navy embroidery. Team with sandals for a chic day look.
Fabric: 100% Cotton
Care: Dry Clean only

title: Ulla Johnson
text:
Another stunning piece from Ulla Johnson hits the store this season. The Anja Dress is a pretty floral printed cotton midi dress. Crinkle cotton detailing with intricate picot edging and ruffle detailing. Split neck with handmade tassels, flutter sleeves, cinching sides and prairie skirt.
Fabric: 100% Cotton
Care: Hand wash

title: Sole and Mare Sunglasses
text:
With a directional hexagonal shape and inspired by Italian design, the Sole and Mare (Sun and Sea) has a contrast laminated design with cut out details on the temple. Handmade tortoise acetate with dark tortoise arms. Brown gradient lenses, CAT 3 Gold P inlay, hinge and printing.
Fabric: German OBE rubber dipped straws, Custom pared packaging feauturing box, pouch and microfibre pouch. One year warranty with proof of purchase.
Frame Measurements:
Lens Height 48mm
Lens Width 52mm
Nosebridge 21mm
Temple 141mm
